Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:29.44,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:40.95,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}The music dance and sing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:44.79,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}They make the children really ring
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:50.24,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}I spend the day your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:56.81,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.47,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}In and around the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:04.63,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Mountains come out of the sky and they stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:11.39,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}One mile over we'll be there and we'll see you
